    public class ClientClusterWideIterator<K,V>
extends AbstractClusterWideIterator<K,V>
implements Iterator<javax.cache.Cache.Entry<K,V>>
    Client side cluster-wide iterator for ICache. This implementation is used by client implementation of JCache. Note: For more information on the iterator details, see AbstractClusterWideIterator.
